ygData.messageBody:
Hey everyone,

Just want to introduce myself. My character is Nance Deventurous
and im a 54 Human cleric. I joined the group so I can gain
knowledge of the game and also get some insights on some zones. A
certain zone I want to know more about is Chardok. I am working on
my epic and wanted to get some information so I can kick overking
bathezed ass. My guild is Method and it rulez! If anyone has any
information on Chardok or would like to group with me sometime and
join my overking raid, please send me a reply. Would love to hear
from you all soon. Later!

Nance Deventurous
Lvl 54 Human Cleric
(Guild) Method
